  "detailed_description": "<strong>Deneb: Across the Stars</strong> is a mouse-only, hardcore platformer game.<br>There are a lot of obstacles but no checkpoints. And a small mistake can lead to an endless fall. Help astronaut Vega overcome all difficulties and find her lost colleague Altair.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016580/extras/2b5e61d866d506f41bd08ae6f7f1f9d9.apng?t=1663509697\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016580/extras/2b5e61d866d506f41bd08ae6f7f1f9d9.poster.avif?t=1663509697\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=252 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple game controls using only the mouse<br></li><li>No checkpoints<br></li><li>Real-time auto-save<br></li><li>Various obstacles designed to make you fall<br></li><li>Gorgeous pixel art graphic<br></li><li>Beautiful soundtrack composed by 50mang<br></li><li>Cute dogs</li></ul><br>Don't get frustrated. The reason we fall is to learn how to pick ourselves up.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016580/extras/239c5fdf66a4be0f501e2d08c7a477a3.poster.avif?t=1663509697\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016580/extras/239c5fdf66a4be0f501e2d08c7a477a3.webm?t=1663509697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016580/extras/239c5fdf66a4be0f501e2d08c7a477a3.mp4?t=1663509697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Deneb: Across the Stars</strong> is a mouse-only, hardcore platformer game.<br>There are a lot of obstacles but no checkpoints. And a small mistake can lead to an endless fall. Help astronaut Vega overcome all difficulties and find her lost colleague Altair.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016580/extras/2b5e61d866d506f41bd08ae6f7f1f9d9.apng?t=1663509697\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016580/extras/2b5e61d866d506f41bd08ae6f7f1f9d9.poster.avif?t=1663509697\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=252 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple game controls using only the mouse<br></li><li>No checkpoints<br></li><li>Real-time auto-save<br></li><li>Various obstacles designed to make you fall<br></li><li>Gorgeous pixel art graphic<br></li><li>Beautiful soundtrack composed by 50mang<br></li><li>Cute dogs</li></ul><br>Don't get frustrated. The reason we fall is to learn how to pick ourselves up.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016580/extras/239c5fdf66a4be0f501e2d08c7a477a3.poster.avif?t=1663509697\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016580/extras/239c5fdf66a4be0f501e2d08c7a477a3.webm?t=1663509697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016580/extras/239c5fdf66a4be0f501e2d08c7a477a3.mp4?t=1663509697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
